org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotML
Interface CameraSystem

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ImageSensorSystem, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, RoboticSystem, SensorSystem, System
All Known Implementing Classes:
CameraSystemImpl
public interface CameraSystem
extends ImageSensorSystem

A representation of the model object 'Camera System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Width
  • Height
  • Alpha u
  • Alpha v
  • U0
  • V0
  • Color format

See Also:
RobotMLPackage.getCameraSystem()
